      </a>
      <a href="/services/dryer-repair/not-tumbling/" class="related-card">
        <h3>Dryer Not Tumbling</h3>
        <p>Drum won't turn but motor hums. Belt, motor, drum rollers, idler pulley.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services/dryer-repair/wont-start/" class="related-card">
        <h3>Dryer Won't Start</h3>
        <p>Dead at the door. Door switch, thermal fuse, start switch, control board.</p>
