      <a href="/services/dryer-vent-repair/" class="related-card">
        <h3>Dryer Vent Repair</h3>
        <p>Full vent run inspection, replacement, and re-routing if needed.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/credentials/licensed/" class="related-card">
        <h3>License and Credentials</h3>
        <p>BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410, BBB Accredited Business.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 08 BOTTOM CTA -->
<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Dryer running 2 to 3 cycles? Vent might be more than a performance issue.</h2>
    <p>Same-day vent clearance and long-cycle diagnostic across LA, OC, Ventura. We treat every long-cycle call as a fire-prevention visit. $89 residential diagnostic, waived with service. BHGS #A49573 and BBB Accredited Business.</p>
